The theoretical foundation derives from:
- Einstein & Freud (1933). Why War? International Institute of Intellectual Cooperation.
- Universal Declaration of Human Rights (1948). United Nations General Assembly.
- Hicks, D. (2011). Dignity: Its Essential Role in Resolving Conflict. Yale University Press.
- Penrose, R. & Hameroff, S. (2014). Consciousness in the universe. Physics of Life Reviews.

Psychometric instruments referenced (not included — cited for attribution):
- PAD Model: Mehrabian & Russell (1974)
- Big Five / OCEAN: Costa & McCrae (1992)
- NASA-TLX: Hart & Staveland (1988)
- UWES: Schaufeli et al. (2002)
- JD-R: Bakker & Demerouti (2007)
- Flow: Csikszentmihalyi (1990)
- Levels of Automation: Sheridan & Verplank (1978); Parasuraman, Sheridan, & Wickens (2000)

